WEBVTT

00:01:28.792 --> 00:01:30.851
get married or divorced,

00:01:30.875 --> 00:01:32.684
or sell real estate.

00:01:32.708 --> 00:01:34.292
That's pretty much it.

00:01:36.208 --> 00:01:39.809
So, that's why don't freak out

00:01:39.833 --> 00:01:41.934
when I tell you that every year

00:01:41.958 --> 00:01:45.851
I can't wait to start
doing my tax declaration.

00:01:45.875 --> 00:01:46.893
(Laughter)

00:01:46.917 --> 00:01:48.934
Because all I have to do

00:01:48.958 --> 00:01:51.059
is sit on my couch with a mobile phone,

00:01:51.083 --> 00:01:55.101
swipe a few pages with prefilled data
on income and deductions

00:01:55.125 --> 00:01:56.809
and hit submit.

00:01:56.833 --> 00:01:58.393
After three minutes,

00:01:58.417 --> 00:02:01.059
I'm looking at the tax return amount.